have 20 children between them (five are Mel Gibson's, three are
Kevin Costner's.) And one more (Selleck's) is on the way.
   Cher, 42, the Oscar-winning actress, is known both for her
devotion to motherhood and her romance with 24-year-old Rob
Camilletti. Swayze, 36, a former ballet dancer, lives with his wife
of 12 years, Lisa Niemi, on a ranch near Los Angeles.
   The other winners, in order:
   2. Jane Seymour, 37; Tom Cruise, 26.
