   6. Madonna, the Material Girl, who turned 30 this year; Tom
Selleck, 43.
   7. Donna Mills, 44; Rob Lowe, 24.
   8. Meg Ryan, 27; Don Johnson, 38.
   9. Jennifer Grey, 28; George Michael, no age given.
   10. Demi Moore, 25; Dennis Quaid, 34.
