<HEAD>French Woman Arrested, Ordered Expelled</HEAD>
<DATELINE>SAN SALVADOR, El Salvador (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Authorities detained a
Frenchwoman for 48 hours before ordering her expelled for carrying
what they called subversive propaganda, the woman, Beatrice Marie
Chantal, said Wednesday.
   She spoke to journalists at Treasury Police headquarters before
being released to French consulate authorities. She was expected to
