government.
   Ms. Chantal said a Salvadoran acquaintance gave her two sealed
envelopes with the material for delivery to a French journalist in
Paris, and that she had not been aware of their content.
   She described herself as a lay missionary and said she had been
in El Salvador for a year working with the Roman Catholic Church's
health commission.
