<TEXT>
   The stock market headed higher in light trading
today, struggling to break its recent stalemate.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials rose 5.15 to 2,090.68 in
the first half hour of trading.
   Gainers outnumbered losers by about 5 to 4 in the overall tally
of New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 443 up, 357 down and
