themselves before they can get a clearer idea of where government
economic policy is headed after the election of a new president.
   Among today's early volume leaders, Coca-Cola rose \ to 43{;
Digital Equipment gained ] to 95}; J.C. Penney picked up } to 50},
and American Telephone & Telegraph dropped [ to 25}.
