   The stock market staged a broad advance today,
bidding to break its recent stalemate.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials climbed 26.49 points to
2,112.02 by 2 p.m. on Wall Street.
   Gainers outnumbered losers by more than 2 to 1 in the overall
